Perceptor/Nightlight:

Nightlight, now reprogramed, started to woke up; Perceptor walked to 
the table and said "Yesss, yesss"hissed the male "Awake, sweet 
Nightlight, awake for your new fate... Now you will need a new name 
for you new life... What will be????" Perceptor opened com link to 
Hydras "MAster Hydras, our new Predacons is awakening... I wonder if 
you desire... be the first to welcome her... Plus, may I suggest 
that she has a small train?  I don't know what are her battle 
skills...."

After that com link Perceptor retired the ties that bound Nightlight
